---
title: Spicy Honey Chicken with Cumin-Roasted Carrots & Cilantro Lime Rice
description: Boneless and skinless does not mean flavorless, at least not in the hands of our chefs. They’re always brainstorming ways to make “chicken for dinner” a little more awesome. The delicious twist this week: a truly magical pan sauce. Hot honey, lime juice, rich chicken stock, and butter mingle to create a condiment you’ll want to drizzle over everything (and now you can!). Speaking of, we’re serving up cumin-spiced carrots and cilantro lime rice on the side. Get ready for your mind to be blown.
